product.name: End2End Nutrition Natural Amla Extract Vitamin C with Zinc for Immunity, Skin Care
product.description:
SKIN HEALTH – Vitamin C needs no introduction when it comes to Skin Health. As an Antioxidant, one of main function of Vitamin C is protecting and Nourishing the Skin. It helps you get Glowing Skin by slowing down Skin Aging, Preventing Sun Damage and Removing Dark Spots & Acne. Vitamin C stimulates your Body’s natural Collagen production. Healthy Collagen levels provide your Skin with a more Youthful appearance.
BOOSTS IMMUNITY – Vitamin C is an essential Nutrient for the Growth and Repair of Tissue all over the Body. It helps to fight the free radicals in the body and it is also involved in various Biochemical processes related to Immune Health. Vitamin C, simply put it helps to build up your Immune System by stimulating the white blood cells, which fights off infections.

product.description:
Reduces Acidity and Relieves Constipation: This product is formulated and can help alleviate acidity-related discomfort and can also provide relief from constipation, promoting a more comfortable digestive experience.
Digestion of Heavy Foods: Sometimes, rich or heavy foods can be hard to digest. Complete Digestive Care contains ingredients that can assist your body in breaking down these foods, making digestion smoother and more efficient.
